name: sidestream-Climb NAKED
summary: This is a spin-off version of the sidestream art project "sidestream-Climb" that supports Meta Quest's Passthrough mode.  By mixing real and virtual in the play environment, we have expanded the art world of sidestream and succeeded in bringing a fantastic and chaotic art play experience to users.  "Sidestream-Climb Naked" is a VR collaboration expansion work between graphic artist "MITSUME" and global techno musician "KEN ISHII".
